00:15:31.560 --> 00:15:33.560
Allah is more powerful than us.

00:15:33.560 --> 00:15:34.560
So Allah says,

00:15:34.560 --> 00:15:36.560
Quraish was given a gift.

00:15:36.560 --> 00:15:38.560
They used to travel north and south

00:15:38.560 --> 00:15:42.560
