00:15:42.560 --> 00:15:44.560
That was a sign of Allah to say

00:15:44.560 --> 00:15:46.560
Quraish is a chosen clan.

00:15:46.560 --> 00:15:49.560
They used to travel north and south.

00:15:49.560 --> 00:15:50.560
And Allah says,

00:15:51.560 --> 00:15:53.560
Allah is making mention of their taming.

00:15:53.560 --> 00:15:56.560
The fact that they could go with all peace

00:15:56.560 --> 00:15:58.560
without worry of what would happen to our caravans.

00:15:58.560 --> 00:16:00.560
Nobody touched their caravans.

00:16:00.560 --> 00:16:01.560
Allahu Akbar.

00:16:01.560 --> 00:16:03.560
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:16:03.560 --> 00:16:05.560
grant us such that our wealth

00:16:05.560 --> 00:16:07.560
