00:16:07.560 --> 00:16:08.560
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:16:08.560 --> 00:16:10.560
protect it for us, preserve it for us.

00:16:10.560 --> 00:16:12.560
Make it sustenance of mercy,

00:16:12.560 --> 00:16:13.560
sustenance of goodness

00:16:13.560 --> 00:16:15.560
and not sustenance that brings about

00:16:15.560 --> 00:16:19.560
or brings with it lots of destruction and arrogance.

00:16:19.560 --> 00:16:21.560
Ameen.

00:16:21.560 --> 00:16:23.560
So Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:16:23.560 --> 00:16:25.560
