00:16:56.560 --> 00:16:58.560
When you borrow, what happens to you?

00:16:58.560 --> 00:16:59.560
Allahu Akbar.

00:16:59.560 --> 00:17:02.560
May Allah safeguard us and not enslave us.

00:17:02.560 --> 00:17:04.560
