00:17:14.560 --> 00:17:15.560
Allahu Akbar.

00:17:15.560 --> 00:17:17.560
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala open our doors.

00:17:17.560 --> 00:17:19.560
So, they had a lot of interest.

00:17:19.560 --> 00:17:21.560
Also, they had festivals.

00:17:21.560 --> 00:17:23.560
Some known as Ukaz and Mijannah

00:17:23.560 --> 00:17:24.560
