00:17:26.560 --> 00:17:28.560
after the month of Shawwal

00:17:28.560 --> 00:17:29.560
or in the month of Shawwal,

00:17:29.560 --> 00:17:31.560
Dhul-Qidah and Dhul-Hijjah

00:17:31.560 --> 00:17:32.560
in such a way that

