00:47:23.590 --> 00:47:25.590
it is reported that just there,

00:47:25.590 --> 00:47:29.590
was the birth place of Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم,

00:47:29.590 --> 00:47:32.590
it was the house of Abu Talib,

00:47:32.590 --> 00:47:35.590
because his father had passed away,

00:47:35.590 --> 00:47:39.590
when he was 7 months in his mother's womb,

00:47:39.590 --> 00:47:43.590
and the father was 25 years old, very young,

00:47:43.590 --> 00:47:46.590
if you take a careful look at what the historians say,

00:47:46.590 --> 00:47:48.590
they say Allah took this man away,

00:47:48.590 --> 00:47:54.590
after his seed was planted into the mother of Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم,

00:47:54.590 --> 00:47:57.590
his job in this dunya was over,

00:47:57.590 --> 00:47:59.590
his job in the world was over,

00:47:59.590 --> 00:48:02.590
and he passed away 25 years old,

00:48:02.590 --> 00:48:04.590
whilst Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم

00:48:04.590 --> 00:48:07.590
was 7 months in the womb of his mother,

00:48:07.590 --> 00:48:11.590
and his mother Amina binti Wahab Ibn Abdi Manaf,

00:48:11.590 --> 00:48:14.590
who was also from the similar clan of Quraysh,

00:48:14.590 --> 00:48:16.590
