00:48:16.590 --> 00:48:18.590
it was the easiest,

00:48:18.590 --> 00:48:22.590
the easiest gestation period,

00:48:22.590 --> 00:48:24.590
the pregnancy was simple,

00:48:24.590 --> 00:48:25.590
I didn't feel anything,

00:48:25.590 --> 00:48:28.590
the childbirth was absolutely easy,

00:48:28.590 --> 00:48:30.590
as though I didn't even give birth,

00:48:30.590 --> 00:48:31.590
Subhanallah,

00:48:31.590 --> 00:48:35.590
the most blessed of all creatures was just being born,

00:48:35.590 --> 00:48:37.590
we want to go into the moment of birth,

00:48:37.590 --> 00:48:39.590
Insha'Allah in a few moments,

00:48:39.590 --> 00:48:45.590
so Allah سبحانه وتعالى caused the death of the father of Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم

