in Madinah Munawwarah,

00:48:47.590 --> 00:48:48.590
did you know that,

00:48:48.590 --> 00:48:50.590
he passed away in Madinah Munawwarah,

00:48:50.590 --> 00:48:51.590
he was gone to Sham,

00:48:51.590 --> 00:48:54.590
and he came back to meet some of his relatives in Madinah,

00:48:54.590 --> 00:48:57.590
and on his way back he passed away in Madinah Munawwarah,

00:48:57.590 --> 00:49:00.590
Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم went back there,

00:49:00.590 --> 00:49:02.590
at the later stage in his life,

00:49:02.590 --> 00:49:05.590
so Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم,

