00:49:23.590 --> 00:49:25.590
صلى الله عليه وسلم,

00:49:25.590 --> 00:49:29.590
pure, already circumcised,

00:49:29.590 --> 00:49:33.590
and his umbilical cord was already separated,

00:49:33.590 --> 00:49:34.590
صلى الله عليه وسلم,

00:49:34.590 --> 00:49:37.590
this is made mention by most of the narrations,

00:49:37.590 --> 00:49:38.590
some of them say,

00:49:38.590 --> 00:49:42.590
