00:49:42.590 --> 00:49:43.590
and some say,

00:49:43.590 --> 00:49:46.590
Abdul Muttalib did it seven days later,

00:49:46.590 --> 00:49:49.590
and he had fed a few people,

00:49:49.590 --> 00:49:51.590
in happiness of a grandchild being born,

00:49:51.590 --> 00:49:54.590
and he had already known in his heart and mind,

00:49:54.590 --> 00:49:56.590
this child is going to be someone great,

00:49:56.590 --> 00:49:58.590
