00:50:01.590 --> 00:50:03.590
from Allah سبحانه وتعالى,

00:50:03.590 --> 00:50:05.590
but they knew he's going to come,

00:50:05.590 --> 00:50:07.590
and something great is going to happen,

00:50:07.590 --> 00:50:08.590
Aminah binti Wahab,

00:50:08.590 --> 00:50:11.590
the mother of Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم says,

00:50:11.590 --> 00:50:14.590
that when I was expecting Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم,

00:50:14.590 --> 00:50:15.590
