00:50:24.590 --> 00:50:26.590
and on that day it is reported that,

00:50:26.590 --> 00:50:30.590
the fire that was worshipped by the Persians in Iran,

00:50:30.590 --> 00:50:32.590
was extinguished and they had to rekindle it,

00:50:32.590 --> 00:50:34.590
Allahu Akbar,

00:50:34.590 --> 00:50:36.590
