00:50:53.590 --> 00:50:55.590
and they had to rebuild it,

00:50:55.590 --> 00:50:56.590
Subhanallah,

00:50:56.590 --> 00:50:57.590
and this was all signs,

00:50:57.590 --> 00:50:59.590
these were signs later on,

00:50:59.590 --> 00:51:01.590
