00:51:27.590 --> 00:51:29.590
but what is more important is,

00:51:29.590 --> 00:51:30.590
what are you doing now,

00:51:30.590 --> 00:51:32.590
before you get to that condition,

00:51:32.590 --> 00:51:34.590
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant us all a good day,

00:51:34.590 --> 00:51:36.590
so the same applies here,

00:51:36.590 --> 00:51:37.590
things happened,

00:51:37.590 --> 00:51:38.590
and later on,

00:51:38.590 --> 00:51:40.590
they were to come to reality,

00:51:40.590 --> 00:51:42.590
so Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wa sallam,

00:51:42.590 --> 00:51:43.590
as we said,

00:51:43.590 --> 00:51:45.590
umbilical cord separated,

00:51:45.590 --> 00:51:46.590
already circumcised,

00:51:46.590 --> 00:51:47.590
Subhanallah,

00:51:47.590 --> 00:51:48.590
he came down,

00:51:48.590 --> 00:51:50.590
looking up to the heavens,

00:51:50.590 --> 00:51:52.590
and one narration actually makes mention,

