00:52:01.590 --> 00:52:03.590
don't worship anyone else,

00:52:03.590 --> 00:52:05.590
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant us,

00:52:05.590 --> 00:52:08.590
the tawfiq and the acceptance,

00:52:08.590 --> 00:52:10.590
to worship him and him alone,

00:52:10.590 --> 00:52:11.590
and then,

00:52:11.590 --> 00:52:13.590
Subhanallah,

00:52:13.590 --> 00:52:14.590
his mother says,

00:52:15.590 --> 00:52:17.590
the grandfather Abdul Muttalib

00:52:17.590 --> 00:52:18.590
loved him so much,

00:52:18.590 --> 00:52:20.590
he was sitting where the Kaaba was,

00:52:20.590 --> 00:52:23.590
and I covered him with a utensil,

