00:52:28.590 --> 00:52:30.590
Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wa sallam,

00:52:30.590 --> 00:52:31.590
when he came,

00:52:31.590 --> 00:52:33.590
by the time we looked back at him,

00:52:33.590 --> 00:52:36.590
that utensil was already broken into two,

00:52:36.590 --> 00:52:38.590
and he was there,

00:52:38.590 --> 00:52:39.590
Subhanallah,

00:52:39.590 --> 00:52:41.590
and the grandfather was so happy,

00:52:41.590 --> 00:52:42.590
so happy,

00:52:42.590 --> 00:52:44.590
that his father had already passed away,

00:52:44.590 --> 00:52:46.590
and he made him a man,

00:52:46.590 --> 00:52:47.590
he made him a young boy,

00:52:47.590 --> 00:52:48.590
who was very close to him,

00:52:48.590 --> 00:52:49.590
and Insha'Allah,

00:52:49.590 --> 00:52:50.590
tomorrow,

00:52:50.590 --> 00:52:51.590
we will look at the other miracles

00:52:51.590 --> 00:52:53.590
of Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wa sallam,

00:52:53.590 --> 00:52:54.590
when he was born,

00:52:54.590 --> 00:52:55.590
what had happened,

00:52:55.590 --> 00:52:56.590
how he grew up,

00:52:56.590 --> 00:52:57.590
and where he was sent,

00:52:57.590 --> 00:52:58.590
and what happened thereafter,

00:52:58.590 --> 00:52:59.590
Insha'Allah,

00:52:59.590 --> 00:53:00.590
we will look at that.

00:53:00.590 --> 00:53:01.590
Before I end,

00:53:01.590 --> 00:53:02.590
I need to make mention of one point,

00:53:02.590 --> 00:53:04.590
there are many people of today,

00:53:04.590 --> 00:53:06.590
who have fabricated certain miracles,

00:53:06.590 --> 00:53:08.590
they say this happened and that happened,

00:53:08.590 --> 00:53:10.590
I want to mention two or three of them,

00:53:10.590 --> 00:53:11.590
so that we know,

00:53:11.590 --> 00:53:14.590
there is no need for us to fabricate anything,

00:53:14.590 --> 00:53:16.590
because what is correct is already there,

00:53:16.590 --> 00:53:18.590
and the miracles have already happened,

00:53:18.590 --> 00:53:20.590
so why should we then fabricate,

00:53:20.590 --> 00:53:23.590
it only drops the value of the story,

00:53:23.590 --> 00:53:25.590
I heard one of the scholars say,

00:53:25.590 --> 00:53:26.590
one of the people say,

00:53:26.590 --> 00:53:27.590
that you know at the time,

00:53:27.590 --> 00:53:31.590
Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wa sallam was born,

00:53:31.590 --> 00:53:33.590
the minarets of the haram made sajda,

00:53:33.590 --> 00:53:34.590
but brother,

00:53:34.590 --> 00:53:35.590
there were no minarets at the time,

00:53:35.590 --> 00:53:36.590
you need to know that,

00:53:36.590 --> 00:53:38.590
and then they said,

00:53:38.590 --> 00:53:39.590
I've heard them say also,

00:53:39.590 --> 00:53:41.590
that the golden stand,

00:53:41.590 --> 00:53:44.590
where Maqam Ibrahim is got up and made sajda,

00:53:44.590 --> 00:53:46.590
brother there was no golden stand at the time,

00:53:46.590 --> 00:53:47.590
so let's not fool each other,

00:53:47.590 --> 00:53:50.590
may Allah sallallahu alayhi wa sallam grant us,

00:53:50.590 --> 00:53:51.590
the mahabba,

00:53:51.590 --> 00:53:53.590
the love of Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wa sallam,

00:53:53.590 --> 00:53:54.590
the best of creation,

00:53:54.590 --> 00:53:58.590
imagine the moment when he came onto the earth,

00:53:58.590 --> 00:54:00.590
so many things across the globe had happened,

00:54:00.590 --> 00:54:02.590
which are absolutely authentic,

00:54:02.590 --> 00:54:04.590
which he makes mention of later on,

00:54:04.590 --> 00:54:06.590
we ask Allah sallallahu alayhi wa sallam,

00:54:06.590 --> 00:54:08.590
to make us appreciative of the fact,

00:54:08.590 --> 00:54:10.590
that we are part of the ummah,

00:54:10.590 --> 00:54:11.590
who have accepted all the prophets,

00:54:11.590 --> 00:54:13.590
Jesus may peace be upon him,

00:54:13.590 --> 00:54:14.590
Moses may peace be upon him,

00:54:14.590 --> 00:54:16.590
Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wa sallam,

00:54:16.590 --> 00:54:17.590
and all of them,

00:54:17.590 --> 00:54:18.590
we respect them,

00:54:18.590 --> 00:54:19.590
and we say,

00:54:19.590 --> 00:54:20.590
may peace be upon them all,

00:54:20.590 --> 00:54:21.590
and may peace be upon us,

00:54:21.590 --> 00:54:22.590
until we meet again,

00:54:22.590 --> 00:54:23.590
wa sallallahu wa sallam,

00:54:23.590 --> 00:54:25.590
wa baraka ala nabina Muhammad,

00:54:25.590 --> 00:54:26.590
subhanallah wa bihamdihi,

00:54:26.590 --> 00:54:27.590
subhanaka allahum wa bihamdik,

00:54:27.590 --> 00:54:29.590
nashhadu alla ilaha illa anta,

00:54:29.590 --> 00:54:31.590
nastaghfiruka wa natubu ilayk.
